, MINDORO (photos), PALAWAN. Notes: (150-)500-2600m. Native.", "distribution": "Australia, Borneo, China, India, Java, Laos, Malay Peninsula, Myanmar, New Caledonia, New Guinea, Pacific Ocean, Philippines, Ryukyu Isls, Solomon Isls, Sulawesi, Sumatra, Taiwan, Thailand, Vietnam. CEBU (photos), LUZON: Bataan (photos), Bulacan, Rizal, MINDANAO: Bukidnon (photos), MINDORO, PALAWAN.", "notes": "0-2600m.", "conservation_status": "", "dao_category": "", "other_fields": {}, "gallery_url": "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/bhbase/cubic_gallery_public.pl?start_at=0&taxon_name=Balanophora+fungosa", "thumbs": ["http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/4_4_11/4apr11/Balanophorafungosa.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaFemales.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaFemales4.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaPollen1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaPollen2.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaStyles.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/1_31_12_4/Upload31Jan2012f/BalanophoraFungosaTuber.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/9_14_12/14sep12/Balanophora1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/9_14_12/14sep12/Balanophora2.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/9_14_12/14sep12/Balanophora5.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/9_14_12/14sep12/Balanophora4.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.ed